    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一条短暂的猫咪观光铁路。历时五年手绘完成。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沿着山间铁路生活的猫咪都有要去的地方。你作为唯一驾驶电车的猫咪，肩负着运送他们的愉悦职责。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个历时五年打造的手绘世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完美适合想要放松的你</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >短暂而甜蜜</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在全新的定时模式中赢得高分</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Short Trip》是由我，Alexander Perrin 所创作的互动插图。使用左右箭头键驾驶一辆观光电车穿越宁静的手绘山景，沿途接送猫咪乘客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187700/extras/498de53383b05c0416414912aa043b30.poster.avif?t=1768097713\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187700/extras/498de53383b05c0416414912aa043b30.webm?t=1768097713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187700/extras/498de53383b05c0416414912aa043b30.mp4?t=1768097713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自首次免费发布以来，《Short Trip》已受到数百万玩家喜爱。此次的完整版包含了原版的所有内容，同时新增了一个“定时”模式，能够与你的电脑时钟同步来创建电车时刻表。按时到达每个车站，并积累高分！我还为好奇的玩家提供了一些关于开发过程的幕后花絮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款“慢节奏”游戏，旨在帮助玩家放松身心，摆脱一天的忙碌所带来的压力。希望您喜欢这趟旅行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187700/extras/d7e0d6902713268bb1ef97bb6f095398.poster.avif?t=1768097713\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187700/extras/d7e0d6902713268bb1ef97bb6f095398.webm?t=1768097713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187700/extras/d7e0d6902713268bb1ef97bb6f095398.mp4?t=1768097713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>关于我</u><br> 我是一位居住在澳大利亚的艺术家，热衷于精密的动态表现、细致的数字渲染技巧以及猫咪（《Short Trip》是这三者的体现）。作为 2pt Interactive 的其中一人，我也制作独立游戏。</p>",
